Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:10.69,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3}翻譯：被T射線銀河光束打敗的馬 濔濔還是喜歡塔科特君 諾·潤潤你又黑了 校對：諾 時間：影·mamo快被壓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王之柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見王之柱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\fn微軟雅黑}sāmekh為腓尼基文字母 對應拉丁文的X
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sāmekh復活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團第二隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Banishing Age」代表人 首領 到場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 綺羅星十字團總會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想諸位已經都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 這座島嶼的天空被王之柱貫穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新籐諏訪與cybody「sāmekh」進行了Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將事態引致此地步的  第三隊「Bougainvilleae」的責任重大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是隨時都有可能發動Apprivoiser的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而碰巧選在昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是我們「Bougainvilleae」的責任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今最重要的事情是他的現狀如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據所殘存的資料來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去所有駕駛過sāmekh的Drivers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在王之柱出現後再也沒有睜開過雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 與死了沒什麼區別 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說 已經停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 我們有必要去確認新籐諏訪的現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然sāmekh的Driver已經覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們綺羅星十字團也必須考慮應對之策了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是視他為敵 事情可就很棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這也算是由Everonu的失誤造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就讓「Bougainvilleae」負起這個責任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就負責到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你擅長的游泳技能盡情展現出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:05:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 我也對他們抱有期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天社團休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 因為剛才聽到你在講話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在練習獨角戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去喝杯咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子好像從黎明前開始就一個人在入海口做禱告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在祈禱諏訪君早點醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這麼要好的三人小組的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這種地方沒有關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為諏訪 也為和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然很擔心但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很擔心但是……但是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我能做的是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實說不定根本不是三人小組
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是兩個人和一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計你已經無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和那兩個人做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起塔科特君 我與那兩個人相處的時間更長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著無法想像的沉重命運的他們如何才能得到幸福？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我很難想像那兩人在現實中獲得幸福的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們終究無法應付自己所背負的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 自從你來到這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你們三個人那麼要好之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得他們兩人得到幸福的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就存在於你們三個好友間的快樂笑容之中麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始這麼認為了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來幹大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂青春的謳歌吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然能來這裡真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你們我就這麼認為了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的救命恩人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子好像很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有像塔科特這樣的人出現在這個島上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙的cybody 我會全部摧毀的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在一定能為那兩人做點什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是待在他們身邊也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都會有非常難受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都想要朋友陪在身邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他們來說你就是這種朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他們不願這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的靈魂深處也一定如此希望著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆都不太會表達自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也不過是島上長大的鄉下人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 銀河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是和子的……和子的奶奶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候得到道伯恩印記的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約一年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找和子的話在入海口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心……不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想見和子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著天體伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到轉瞬即逝的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}如今的一切都在黑白畫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟吧 電力柩！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}悄然凍結的白色吐息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}壓抑在心的話語化為有形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}只有聚集那份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}才能為天空籠上光明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}被悲傷浸染的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}嚮往重疊的純白色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}傳遞著通向未來的無限溫柔的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}在無人知曉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}等待黎明的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零空間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:13:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}滿載光輝踏上旅途的我有著無可預測的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}飄舞的雪花是星之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然會出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說與sāmekh進行Apprivoiser後還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}向著天體伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}深信著轉瞬即逝的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}如今的一切都在黑白畫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是昨晚戰爭的延續！銀河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是昨晚的那傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪他……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apprivoiser
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}讓這笑容衝破烏雲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}就讓我滿載著愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}飛向天空的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}各自踏上征途的旅人們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}或許素未謀面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}安眠時分所見夢想的殘像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯爽登場 銀河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H4D1F0A&\be3\blur3}一切仍定格在黑白記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道伯恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除外來人員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我們的島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的遺跡一切都是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個人偶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游動吧！美人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛下去了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂吧！Τ射線銀河光束！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會又暴走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經醒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！和子 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這副打扮 要到哪裡去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏加！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在零空間裡 諏訪醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在宅子裡找找！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須快點去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王說要讓出王位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王本來就打算把王位讓給
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻上能解開詛咒之藍血的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Sam拒絕了那個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王 我只想要你的那艘「銀河之船」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想乘上它駛向光彩奪目的銀河的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不需要王位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想要國家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了小魚的故事 我又能好好加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 國王說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾向你保證 不論你想要什麼我都給
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘「銀河之船」就讓給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 年輕人啊 「刺殺烏賊的Sam」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用心聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要啟動那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有將你所喜歡的少女的鮮血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一滴不剩的 全部注入引擎裡才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有殺死你心愛的少女才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就無法啟動那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始那就是你的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜啊 這顆糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為人生的冒險仍在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新籐諏訪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們綺羅星十字團為了邀請您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺羅星十字團 第一隊Emperor隊長的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正虛席恭候您前來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不覺得他有點兒怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有意識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河美少年 你別靠近！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪 諏訪 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 他想使用王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回平時的諏訪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你幹的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打了我是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 想死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:30.38,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢動いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:30.38,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想開始悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.80,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人の鼓動触れた時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.80,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們觸碰到彼此的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:42.67,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　今誰を思っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:42.67,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在想念誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:50.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝子星に眺めた切ないその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:50.41,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過玻璃星星看到你的側臉 讓人如此無法割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:56.65,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微かな距離でも届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:56.65,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使近在咫尺 卻也無法向你傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:01.25,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言い訳ばっかりを束ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:01.25,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出種種借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:04.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:04.21,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避著現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:07.60,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱虫だったあの頃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:07.60,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我如此膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:15.60,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れそうな弱さと向き合える気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:15.60,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在終於鼓起勇氣直面那潰不成軍的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:19.33,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出すよ 明日の扉開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:19.33,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧 打開通向明天的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:23.00,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が居る場所まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:23.00,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往你所在的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:30.18,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃し続けてきた思い伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:30.18,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你傾訴那份一直未說出口的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:37.47,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here in my house君が笑う 何気ない世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:37.47,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這坦誠相對的世界裡 向我微笑
